'Gertjan Mulder', professionally known as 'Brainpower', is a bi-lingual rapper,
who writes, records and performs in both the English as well as the Dutch
language. The Dutch audience mainly knows him as a Dutch language rapper. He was
born in Belgium and grew up in the Netherlands. He started making music in the
eighties, and spent his time making a name for himself in the 90s. Since 2001,
he released five solo studio albums, one Live album CD/DVD set, a book/DVD set,
a Greatest Hits Box Set, and a few other successful side projects.
